1. like this post
2. follow @_sierrasoles_ & myself 
3. comment below your shoe size & tag three friends

each friend you tag gets you one entry. tag as many friends as you want (must be real pages & don’t spam famous people). must be following both pages to be eligible to win. 

giveaway ends 7/2/21 at 11pm pst 
winner selected 7/3/21 at 4pm pst
